title: How to Install a Blackhawk K&N Air Intake
description: Upgrade your under-the-hood appearance, along with your vehicle's overall performance with a Blackhawk K&N Air Intake (part # K&N 71-2545).

asset.title: 2011-2014 Dodge Challenger, Dodge Charger and Chrysler 300 Air Intake Installation
asset.description:
See how easy it is to add more performance to your 2011-2014 Dodge Challenger, Dodge Charger and Chrysler 300 models with this K&N air intake system. 

http://www.knfilters.com/search/product.aspx?prod=71-2545

This intake system created an estimated gain of 9.09 horsepower at 4564 RPM.
